<sentence ID="SENT-22" start="1334" end="1367">We are incorporated in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Maryland</ENAMEX>.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-23" start="1367" end="1494">There are just 5 of us on the board (we
are a charity 501(c)(3), although we all live in different states from coast
to coast.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-24" start="1494" end="1560">It is very difficult to find times for all of us to get <Event TYPE="Contact" SUBTYPE="Meet">together</Event>.</sentence>
<sentence ID="SENT-25" start="1560" end="1658">Would I need to check the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Maryland</ENAMEX> law or the law in the state in which this
board member lives?</sentence>

<sentence ID="SENT-26" start="1658" end="1675">Thanks.</sentence>
    

</POST>
