<sentence ID="SENT-80" start="5505" end="5647">Take a look at any of the large student unions, they all <Event TYPE="Transaction" SUBTYPE="Transfer-Money">pay</Event> their <Event TYPE="Personnel" SUBTYPE="Elect">elected</Event>
